    "content": [
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Wall Dimensions"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "When using CAD to dimension Walls inside scenes at the Drawings Page, there is a trick to get automatic dimensions for a Wall Length or thickness."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "First, select the scene on the Drawings Page and then click the  CAD  button."
        },
        {
            "type": "link",
            "data": {
                "text": "CAD",
                "uuid": "c364cda2-94c1-45c4-950a-125c6e19bd95",
                "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "link",
            "data": {
                "text": "",
                "uuid": "c364cda2-94c1-45c4-950a-125c6e19bd95",
                "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": "image1924.gif",
            "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Next, turn your Snaps off in the  Statusbar Menu ."
        },
        {
            "type": "link",
            "data": {
                "text": "Statusbar Menu",
                "uuid": "ab1790c8-4275-4839-a647-d5a131c27144",
                "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Then, select the  Dimensions     option."
        },
        {
            "type": "link",
            "data": {
                "text": "Dimensions",
                "uuid": "b2e0e61a-3db8-4e05-86e8-8de0e1729d3d",
                "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": "image2091.gif",
            "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Next, set the Dimension to Aligned Tailed."
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": "image2092.gif",
            "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Then, hold your mouse close to the wall that you wish to dimension and hold   +   while you click near the Wall."
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": "ctrl_key.png",
            "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": "shift_key.png",
            "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Pull the dimension away from the Wall until you have it where you want it to be displayed and then click to drop the new dimension line at that point."
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": "image824.gif",
            "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
        }
    ],
